## âœ… How to Run

### 1. Install `yt-dlp` + `ffmpeg`

```bash
pip install yt-dlp
# Or download yt-dlp binary
# Install ffmpeg from https://ffmpeg.org/
```

### 2. Run Server

```bash
go run server.go
```

### 3. Run Client (in same or another machine)

```bash
go run client.go
```

### 4. Open Browser

```
http://localhost:8080
```

